{"word":"H1639 - גָּרַע - gâraʻ - gaw-rah' - Abate","slug":"H1639","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּרַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gâraʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gaw-rah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05E2; - ga&#x0302;ra&#x201B;</b> - <i>gaw-rah'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>scrape</i> off; by implication to <i>shave</i>, <i>remove</i>, <i>lessen</i> or <i>withhold: - </i>abate, clip, (di-) minish, do (take) away, keep back, restrain, make small, withdraw."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4052\">H4052</a>"}]}